<br>
Torch of the Elements - Neh'Ashiir CoM top level, rare drop.  Common drop is Ornate Rune Shield(appealing to casters, easy to find help), area is doable with a group of 6 but is often raided with 12-18.  I suggest signing up for CoM raids that are posted in the Raid: Intention section or possibly hosting your own raid depending on how fast you wanna get it done.  I got mine on a raid where we killed another Lord for the Shaman epic, but its entirely possible to just go straight to him with 6-12.<br>
<br>
